OL,3,CBirmingham MP says Starmer must go as
OL,4,CPM fights off leadership pressure
OL,6,FPaulette Hamilton MP has called on
OL,7,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer to step
OL,8,Fdown, saying voters have "stopped
OL,9,Flistening" to him after Labour's
OL,10,Fbruising local election results.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News Central,
OL,13,FBirmingham Erdington MP said the
OL,14,Fresults showed "confidence has been
OL,15,Flost" in the prime minister's
OL,16,Fleadership and warned that "change now
OL,17,Fmust come from the top".
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@JO]vD@POUwD@EO]xD@\OUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
