CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1778505069
OL,3,CBirmingham MP says Starmer must go as
OL,4,CPM fights off leadership pressure
OL,6,FThe intervention came as Starmer
OL,7,Fdelivered a major speech aimed at
OL,8,Fheading off growing pressure over his
OL,9,Fleadership.
OL,11,FThe prime minister acknowledged
OL,12,Ffrustration among voters after
OL,13,FLabour's difficult local election
OL,14,Fresults, but insisted he would
OL,15,Fcontinue with what he described as his
OL,16,F"10-year project" for the country.
OL,18,F"I know people are frustrated by the
OL,19,Fstate of Britain, frustrated by
OL,20,Fpolitics, and some people, frustrated
OL,21,Fwith me," Starmer said.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@QO]zD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1778505069
OL,3,CBirmingham MP says Starmer must go as
OL,4,CPM fights off leadership pressure
OL,6,F"I know I have my doubters, I know I
OL,7,Fneed to prove them wrong, and I will."
OL,9,FStarmer promised further action on
OL,10,Fdefence, Europe and energy, saying the
OL,11,Fcountry faced "dangerous times" and
OL,12,Fneeded "a bigger response than we
OL,13,Fanticipated in 2024".
OL,15,FThe speech comes ahead of Wednesday's
OL,16,FKing's Speech, which is expected to
OL,17,Fset out the government's priorities
OL,18,Ffor the next parliamentary session.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@fO]sD@OOUsD@_O]tD@HOUuD@TO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
