PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1778505069
OL,3,CBirmingham MP says Starmer must go as
OL,4,CPM fights off leadership pressure
OL,6,FLabour backbencher Catherine West has
OL,7,Falso suggested she could mount a
OL,8,Fleadership challenge if senior
OL,9,Fministers do not move against Starmer,
OL,10,Falthough allies have indicated her
OL,11,Fcampaign is intended to pressure the
OL,12,FCabinet rather than launch a serious
OL,13,Fbid for No 10.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, former deputy prime
OL,16,Fminister Angela Rayner is due to
OL,17,Fdeliver a speech later on Monday after
OL,18,Fwarning the prime minister must "meet
OL,19,Fthe moment and set out the change our
OL,20,Fcountry needs".
OL,26,@zD@aOU|D@NO]
